\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 Loading Soundfiles
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\
To load a soundfile drag one from the finder on to a key, knob or slider. WAV and AIFF files are supported, not MP3 or any other.\
\
You can also shift-click on a key, knob or slider to browse for a file.\
\
You can also drag and drop more than one soundfile to load several files at once. They will spread upwards for as many keys/knobs/sliders as there are files dragged.\
\
It is possible to load more than one soundfile on one key, more on that below.\
\
